in front of the whole town?

17:35.358 --> 17:36.707
[sheepish laugh]

17:36.794 --> 17:38.622
- [laughs]
No problem.

17:38.709 --> 17:40.798
A well-placed hairclip
should do the trick.

17:40.885 --> 17:42.583
- Perfect!

17:44.976 --> 17:48.763
Wait, Sunny, if you don't mind
doing a little more styling,

17:48.850 --> 17:51.809
