some rock star hair too?

17:51.896 --> 17:53.420
- I'd love to!

17:53.507 --> 17:58.338
♪ ♪

17:58.425 --> 18:02.603
A splash of orange,

18:02.690 --> 18:05.345
brush it up,
and comb it out.

18:05.432 --> 18:07.086
- Whoa!

18:07.173 --> 18:09.653
I feel like we should be
getting tickets to see Sunny.

18:09.740 --> 18:12.526
- Nothing says rock star
like music notes,

18:12.613 --> 18:16.530
and a little face paint
for the finishing touch.

18:16.617 --> 18:19.750
- Hey, I look like
a real rock star!

18:19.837 --> 18:22.362
Thank you, Sunny.
- Yeah!

18:22.449 --> 18:24.451
[laughter]

18:24.538 --> 18:26.105
- Smile!
[shutter clicks]

18:26.192 --> 18:29.543
Now that's one
for the Style Files.

18:29.630 --> 18:32.459
crowd: [chanting]
We want The Surf Bros!

18:32.546 --> 18:34.852
- Let's do this!

18:34.939 --> 18:37.942
- They made it!
[cheers and applause]

18:39.466 --> 18:41.381
- Hey, everyone!

18:41.468 --> 18:44.514
Let's get this concert started.
Yes!

18:44.601 --> 18:48.562
- And now, introducing the
newest member of The Surf Bros,

18:48.649 --> 18:50.564
for one time only,

18:50.651 --> 18:54.829
Timmy the recycling and
everything else guy!

18:54.916 --> 18:56.265
- Hit it, Timmy.

18:56.352 --> 18:58.354
- And one, two, three, four!

18:58.441 --> 19:01.357
