20:35.364 --> 20:38.889
- Go Timmy!
- Thank you, Friendly Falls!

20:38.976 --> 20:41.805
And a big thank you
to Lacey and Sunny

20:41.892 --> 20:44.852
for our rockin' styles!

20:44.939 --> 20:47.637
- I guess Sunny did a good job.

20:47.724 --> 20:50.074
- Mm-hmm,
almost as good as us.

20:50.161 --> 20:53.556
