- Surf Bros!

20:53.643 --> 20:56.080
- Way to go, Timmy!
- That was awesome!

20:56.167 --> 20:59.562
- Good job from one
drum master to another.

20:59.649 --> 21:01.216
- Thanks, everyone,

21:01.303 --> 21:04.219
for helping me live out
my rock star dream for a day.

21:04.306 --> 21:07.309
- And thanks for all
you do for us every day.

21:07.396 --> 21:09.485
I sure hope you don't
forget about us

21:09.572 --> 21:11.270
now that you're
a big rock star.

21:11.357 --> 21:13.446
Friendly Falls needs you.

21:13.533 --> 21:15.491
all: Yeah!

21:15.578 --> 21:17.798
- Don't worry.
I'm not going anywhere.

21:17.885 --> 21:19.887
I'd get bored
doing just one job,

21:19.974 --> 21:22.933
